entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: Bib Fortuna had you deal with Romo Vax, a traitor who tried to profit from Jabba's greed. After you dealt with the traitor Bib sent you to speak to Jabba himself.
entries.journal_entry_description: There are plenty of people who live or work in Jabba's Palace who need things done. You're the person to do those things.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Bib Fortuna wants you to speak to Romo Vax, who is in the Wayfar cantina. He has some disks that he is supposed to be delivering to Jabba. Bib wants you to pick them up as Romo is afraid to lead spies into Jabba's Palace.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Romo Vax is convinced that he's being followed by Valarian's thugs. Kill 10 of them to convince him that things are all right.
entries.task02_comm_message_text: Stop spending time working for Romo Vax, you work for me. His information doesn't allow him to make demands. We're through negotiating, if he wants to get paid he turns over the disks now.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Romo Vax's enemies have been destroyed. Return to Romo and demand that he hand the disks over.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Romo Vax lost the disks he was supposed to bring Jabba. He says they were stolen by Valarian's thugs. Kill Valarian's thugs until the disks are all recovered.
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: You have found all of Romo Vax's missing disks. Return them to him so he can sort through them and find the disk he needs to give to Jabba.
entries.task06_journal_entry_description: Now that Romo Vax has found the proper disk, you should deliver it to Bib Fortuna in Jabba's Palace.
entries.task06_journal_entry_title: Take the Disk To Bib Fortuna
entries.task07_journal_entry_description: While Bib decodes the disk from Romo Vax you are to teach the Sennex the lesson they didn't learn before. They've been stirring up trouble. Bib Fortuna wants to remind them who is in charge on Tatooine. Take out 20 Sennex.
entries.task08_comm_message_text: Romo is a Sennex spy! They copied the data you previously stole from the Sennex. It uploaded itself to the holonet! Romo Vax must die! He's at the Sennex Compound. Return when he is no more!
entries.task09_journal_entry_description: Go to the Sennex Compound and kill Romo Vax.
entries.task10_journal_entry_description: Now that Romo Vax is dead, return to Bib Fortuna at Jabba's Palace.
